            <noteGrp type="workDesc">
               <note type="description">Using the same format as Sulamī’s book Maqāmāt al-awliyāʾ, a book of adab, with many stories from al-Andalus and people that IA knew.</note>
               <note type="structure">Structure of Work</note>
